title: Invisible Mom II (Full Movie) Family Comedy

sources.title: Invisible Mom II (Full Movie) Family Comedy
sources.description:
An adopted 12-year-old (Justin Berfield) gets a new brother, a chemist father (Barry Livingston) and a mother (Dee Wallace-Stone) who can disappear at will.

Director: Fred Olen Ray
Writer: Sean O'Bannon (screenplay)
Stars: Dee Wallace, Justin Berfield, Trenton Knight
1999
